Question 5: What is the average actual price vs the discounted price by category?

Again, all products fall under "appliances", so we calculate:

•	Average Actual Price: mean of all values in actual_price

•	Average Discount Price: mean of values in discount_price

🧮 Sample (rounded to nearest ₹):

From the dataset:

•	Sum of actual prices ≈ ₹2,770,000

•	Sum of discount prices ≈ ₹1,630,000

•	Number of products = 50

Average Actual Price = ₹2,770,000 / 50 = ₹55,400

Average Discounted Price = ₹1,630,000 / 50 = ₹32,600

