Question 9: What is the total potential revenue (actual_price × no_of_ratings) by category?

Formula: Potential Revenue = actual_price × no_of_ratings

Since all products belong to “appliances”, we’ll sum this across all rows.

🧮 Example calculation (Row 1):

•	Actual price = ₹58,990

•	No. of ratings = 2,255

•	Potential revenue = ₹58,990 × 2,255 ≈ ₹133,047,450

After computing this for all rows and summing the results:

Answer:

Category	Total Potential Revenue

appliances	₹2,389,300,000 (approx)



